**[The Crime Scene — Initial Description]**
- The GM describes the room: a spacious, circular chamber ringed by a dozen lancet windows, natural light made hazy by a thin haze of tobacco smoke.
- Janussi's corpse lies near the foot of the mahogany desk — a human male around 70, vacant eyes fixed on the ceiling, white robes extremely bloodied at the torso, rib cage caved in, a gaping hollow in the chest.
- A chair is toppled near the desk; a marble statue and its pedestal lie on the ground; candelabra candles have burned entirely to their stubs, leaving a waxy mess; an ink pot has been spilled.
- Blue gemstones and several empty pouches are scattered on the stone floor in front of the safe.
- A wooden staircase leads up to a second floor.

**[GM]** — *reading the room description*
> "You enter a spacious, circular chamber, ringed by a dozen lancet windows that fill the room with natural light, which is made hazy by a thin… bug of tobacco. Lying on the ground near the foot of the chamber's elegant mahogany desk in the center of the room is the corpse of a human male around 70 years old. His vacant eyes fixed on the ceiling, his splendid, flowing white robes are extremely bloodied around the torso, while a closer look reveals that his rib cage has been caved in and there is a gaping hollow in the chest. The wrist of the chamber is in some disorder. A chair has been toppled over near the desk. The desk itself is neatly arranged, with a single book lying open in the center, next to a pile of books on the left. and a stack of notes on the right. But the extinguished candles of the candelabra have burned down to their stub, leaving a waxy mess spilled below them, and an ink pot has been filled. On either side of the room, on the other side of the room, and to the desk, a marble statue and its pedestal lie on the ground. Blue gemstones appear to have been scattered on the stone floor in front of the safe, along with several empty pouches. A wooden set of stairs leads up to the second floor."

**[Thorin]** — *immediate read on the safe area*
> "So it looks like a robbery, like somebody raided the safe, and what they were looking for is more valuable than blue gemstones?"

