**[GM]** — *interpreting the ink layers*
> "It's clearly that he was used to be… the blue ink was the one that he was using most recently. And so that it's… it is interesting that, you know, like, before that, he was using purple ink, and not just before that, weeks ago, before that a day or so ago."

