**[GM]** — *as Tadric, ruling out short candles*
> "she, the, the Tadric says, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, he would never have such… that… that would… that would… Miss Hollypocket would never allow him to spend the night with candles that would fall apart like that. That would be…"

**[Thorin]**
> "So likely, he was murdered quite some time ago."

**[GM]**
> "Right."

