> "It almost… it almost hit 19, and then it just, like, tipped over, and I know that it decided that it was a 1 the minute I pressed the button, but I'm really pissed off that it teased me."

**[Zalthir]** — *medicine check — rolled 17*

**[GM]** — *results of the medicine check*
> "You reveal that the keeper's heart is missing, but no other organs."

**[Zalthir]**
